items.name: SCPP-Stock-Closing-Price-Prediction
items.description: This repository offers a deep learning framework for equity price forecasting using historical market data. It integrates data preprocessing, technical indicator engineering, and neural models (LSTM, BiLSTM, RNN) to capture temporal patterns. Built with Python and libraries like PyTorch, Optuna, and Plotly.
